"zaokrąglany do najbliższej pół godziny."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:748
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Select any open region of time, and double click it or start writing the "
#| "title of the event. &korganizer; will automatically set the duration and "
